acceptance

Class AcceptanceGenericDD

  • java.lang.Object
    • acceptance.AcceptanceGenericDD
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AcceptanceOmegaDD, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class AcceptanceGenericDD
extends java.lang.Object
implements AcceptanceOmegaDD
    A generic acceptance condition (based on JDD state sets). This is an AST of a boolean formula (conjunction and disjunction) over atoms of the form Inf(states), Inf(!states), Fin(states) and Fin(!states).
    Semantics: Inf(states) <=> G F states Inf(!states) <=> G F !states Fin(states) <=> F G !states Fin(!states) <=> F G states
